sorcer.ui.provider

Class SortableTreeNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode
      • sorcer.ui.provider.SortableTreeNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, javax.swing.tree.MutableTreeNode, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode

    public class SortableTreeNode
extends javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode
    Generic tree node class based on DefaultMutableTreeNode. Added features are follow:
    • Adding a child in lexicographical order.
    • Finding a child/descendant node who has specified user object.
    • Managing information about drop-over.
